#!/usr/bin/ruby
#http://www.checkio.org/mission/spaceship-landing-strip/ verifier.

def checkio(data)
	y=data.size
	x=data[0].size
	m=Array.new(y){[0]*x}
	y.times{|j|
		r=0
		x.times{|i|
			#if data[j][i,1]=='.'
			if data[j][i]==1
				r+=1
			else
				r=0
			end
			m[j][i]=r
		}
	}
	r=0
	x.times{|i|
		y.times{|j|
			ma=9999999
			j.step(y-1){|k|
				ma=[ma,m[k][i]].min
				r=[r,ma*(k-j+1)].max
			}
		}
	}
	r
end

if $0==__FILE__
	if false
		while(y,x=gets.split.map(&:to_i))!=[0,0]
			data=y.times.map{gets.chomp}
			puts checkio(data)
		end
	else
		gets.to_i.times{
			data=5.times.map{gets.split.map(&:to_i)}
			puts checkio(data)
			gets
		}
	end
end

### constant

N = 5

### main

m = gets.to_i

m.times do
  flds = []
  N.times do
    line = gets.strip
    line = gets.strip if line.empty?
    flds << line.split.map(&:to_i)
  end
  #p flds

  hsums = N.times.map{[]}

  for y in (0...N)
    prv = 0
    for x in (0...N)
      if flds[y][x] == 1
        prv += 1
        hsums[y][x] = prv
      else
        hsums[y][x] = prv = 0
      end
    end
  end
  #p hsums

  max_rct = 0

  for x in (0...N)
    seq = 0
    minh = N
    for y in (0...N)
      hs = hsums[y][x]
      if hs > 0
        seq += 1
        minh = hs if minh > hs
        rct = seq * minh
        max_rct = rct if max_rct < rct
      else
        seq = 0
        minh = N
      end
    end
  end

  puts max_rct
end

### constant

N = 5

### main

m = gets.to_i

m.times do
  flds = []
  N.times do
    line = gets.strip
    line = gets.strip if line.empty?
    flds << line.split.map(&:to_i)
  end
  #p flds

  hsums = N.times.map{[]}

  for y in (0...N)
    hsums[y][0] = flds[y][0]
    for x in (1...N)
      if flds[y][x] == 1
        hsums[y][x] = hsums[y][x - 1] + 1
      else
        hsums[y][x] = 0
      end
    end
  end
  #p hsums

  max_rct = 0

  for x in (0...N)
    for y in (0...N)
      min_hs = hsums[y][x]
      next if min_hs == 0

      max_rct = min_hs if max_rct < min_hs

      (y - 1).downto(0) do |y0|
        hs0 = hsums[y0][x]
        break if hs0 == 0
        min_hs = hs0 if min_hs > hs0
        rct = min_hs * (y - y0 + 1)
        max_rct = rct if max_rct < rct
      end
    end
  end

  puts max_rct
end
